'''全球化智库'''（{{lang-en|Center for China and Globalization}}，简称'''CCG'''），原名'''中国与全球化智库'''，是[[中国|中国]]一家总部设在[[北京|北京]]的[[智库|智库]]<ref>{{Cite news|last=Allen-Ebrahimian|first=Bethany|date=May 7, 2018|title=Rubio Questions D.C. Panel on China Influence|work=[[Foreign_Policy|Foreign Policy]]|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180508054738/https://foreignpolicy.com/2018/05/07/rubio-questions-d-c-panel-on-china-influence-united-front-beijing-communist-party/|access-date=April 27, 2021}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Citation|last1=Joske|first1=Alex|title=The United Front and Technology Transfer|date=2020-08-03|url=https://www.google.com/books/edition/China_s_Quest_for_Foreign_Technology/K1LzDwAAQBAJ|work=China’s Quest for Foreign Technology|pages=258–274|editor-last=Hannas|editor-first=William C.|edition=1|location=Abingdon, Oxon |publisher=Routledge|language=en|doi=10.4324/9781003035084-20|isbn=978-1-003-03508-4|oclc=1153338764|last2=Stoff|first2=Jeffrey|s2cid=225395399|editor2-last=Tatlow|editor2-first=Didi Kirsten|access-date=2020-11-26|archive-date=2020-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201122225253/https://www.google.com/books/edition/China_s_Quest_for_Foreign_Technology/K1LzDwAAQBAJ|url-status=live}}</ref>根据宾夕法尼亚大学智囊团和公民社会计划（TTCSP）的2020年全球智库指数，CCG在全球100家顶级智库中排名第64位，在“最佳独立智库”中排第37位。<ref>{{Cite journal|last=McGann|first=James|date=2021-01-28|title=2020 Global Go To Think Tank Index Report|url=https://repository.upenn.edu/think_tanks/18|journal=TTCSP Global Go To Think Tank Index Reports|access-date=2021-04-26|archive-date=2021-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210612004515/https://repository.upenn.edu/think_tanks/18/|dead-url=no}}</ref>CCG的学者们经常为《纽约时报》、《金融时报》、彭博新闻社<ref>{{Cite news|last=Wang Huiyao|date=Nov 11, 2020|title=China Shouldn’t Make Biden’s Job Harder|work=[[Bloomberg_Opinion|Bloomberg Opinion]]|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2020-11-11/how-biden-could-improve-u-s-china-relations?sref=FsH7Eprk|access-date=April 21, 2021|archive-date=2021-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411222658/https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2020-11-11/how-biden-could-improve-u-s-china-relations?sref=FsH7Eprk|dead-url=no}}</ref>、《南华早报》、《北京评论》<ref>{{Cite news|last=Wang Huiyao|date=Nov 23, 2020|title=Highlights of China’s diplomacy in the post-pandemic word|work=[[Beijing_Review|Beijing Review]]|url=http://www.bjreview.com/Opinion/Voice/202011/t20201123_800227768.html|access-date=April 21, 2021|archive-date=2021-04-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210406042344/http://www.bjreview.com/Opinion/Voice/202011/t20201123_800227768.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>、CGTN、《中国日报》撰稿，<ref>{{Cite news|last=David Blair|date=November 2, 2020|title=Foreign capital flows can’t be allowed to create asset bubbles|work=[[CGTN|CGTN]]|url=https://www.chinadaily.com.cn/a/202011/02/WS5f9f6cc4a31024ad0ba827fb.html|access-date=April 21, 2021|archive-date=2021-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210423123749/https://www.chinadaily.com.cn/a/202011/02/WS5f9f6cc4a31024ad0ba827fb.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>专家们也经常出现在英国广播公司、德国广播公司、美国有线电视新闻网和美国全国广播公司等通讯社。

== 创始人 ==
CCG由学者[[王辉耀|王辉耀]]和[[苗绿|苗绿]]创立，位列世界百强<ref>{{Cite web|last=McGann|first=James G.|date=January 28, 2021|title=2020 Global Go To Think Tank Index Report|url=https://repository.upenn.edu/cgi/viewcontent.cgi?article=1019&context=think_tanks|access-date=April 27, 2021|archive-date=2021-05-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210522000141/https://repository.upenn.edu/cgi/viewcontent.cgi?article=1019&context=think_tanks|dead-url=no}}</ref>。王辉耀是[[九三学社|九三学社]]中央委员、国务院参事。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://english.counsellor.gov.cn/html/member/WangHuiyao.html|title=Counsellors' Office of the State Council|website=english.counsellor.gov.cn|access-date=2019-10-09|archive-date=2019-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191009162556/http://english.counsellor.gov.cn/html/member/WangHuiyao.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>苗绿是参加2021年慕尼黑安全会议的唯一中国智库代表。<ref>{{Cite news|last=MSC|date=2021|title=MSC Special Edition 2021|work=[[BMSC_2021|BMSC 2021]]|url=https://securityconference.org/en/msc-special-edition-2021|access-date=April 21, 2021|archive-date=2021-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210518215736/https://securityconference.org/en/msc-special-edition-2021/|dead-url=no}}</ref>王辉耀不再在海归学者协会任职。<ref>{{Cite web|last=Western Returned Scholars|date=February 10, 2021|title=President, vice president and board members of the 8th Council of the European and American Association|work=[[Western_Returned_Scholars|Western Returned Scholars]]|url=http://www.wrsa.net/content_41469454.htm|access-date=April 21, 2021|archive-date=2021-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210413224709/http://www.wrsa.net/content_41469454.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 研究领域 ==
CCG的研究覆盖全球化、全球治理、国际经贸与投资、国际关系、人才国际化、企业国际化和智库发展等议题。

== 活动 ==
CCG与诸多国际智库保持交流关系。CCG多次参加慕尼黑安全会议<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://en.ccg.org.cn/html/events/3639.html|title=-Center for China and Globalization|website=en.ccg.org.cn|access-date=2019-10-09|archive-date=2019-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191009161054/http://en.ccg.org.cn/html/events/3639.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>、蒙克辩论<ref>{{Cite news|last=Munk|date=May 9, 2019|title=Munk Debates|work=[[Munk_Debates|Munk Debates]]|url=https://munkdebates.com/debates/china|access-date=April 26, 2021|archive-date=2019-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191227182108/https://munkdebates.com/debates/china|dead-url=no}}</ref>、巴黎和平论坛<ref>{{Cite news|last=Paris Peace Forum|date=Nov 12, 2019|title=Paris Peace Forum|work=[[Paris_Peace_Forum|Paris Peace Forum]]|url=https://parispeaceforum.org/program-2019/|access-date=April 26, 2021|archive-date=2020-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200226140639/https://parispeaceforum.org/program-2019/|dead-url=no}}</ref>、雅典民主论坛<ref>{{Cite news|last=Athens Democracy|date=Nov 12, 2019|title=Athens Democracy Forum|work=[[Athens_Democracy_Forum|Athens Democracy Forum]]|url=https://www.athensdemocracyforum.com/sites/default/files/inline-files/ADF-Conference-Booklet.pdf/|access-date=April 26, 2021|archive-date=2020-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201027202552/https://www.athensdemocracyforum.com/sites/default/files/inline-files/ADF-Conference-Booklet.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>等活动，以及布鲁金斯学会、战略与国际问题研究中心<ref>{{Cite news|last=Bonnie S. Glaser|date=Sep 20, 2010|title=Re-calibrating the BRI: A Conversation with Wang Huiyao|work=[[CSIS|CSIS]]|url=https://www.csis.org/podcasts/chinapower/re-calibrating-bri-conversation-wang-huiyao|access-date=April 26, 2021|archive-date=2021-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210428224224/https://www.csis.org/podcasts/chinapower/re-calibrating-bri-conversation-wang-huiyao|dead-url=no}}</ref>、卡托研究所<ref>{{Cite news|last=Zhang Zhihao|date=Nov 26, 2020|title=Experts: World will prosper from good China-US ties|work=[[CSIS|CSIS]]|url=http://global.chinadaily.com.cn/a/202011/26/WS5fbee1b3a31024ad0ba96778.html|access-date=April 26, 2021|archive-date=2021-04-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210429110156/http://global.chinadaily.com.cn/a/202011/26/WS5fbee1b3a31024ad0ba96778.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>、卡内基国际和平基金会<ref>{{Cite web|last=Philippe le Corre|date=Mar 24, 2020|title=Europe’s Tightrope Diplomacy on China|work=[[Carnegie_Endowment_for_International_Peace|Carnegie Endowment for International Peace]]|url=https://carnegieendowment.org/2021/03/24/europe-s-tightrope-diplomacy-on-china-pub-84159|access-date=April 26, 2021|archive-date=2021-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210426185015/https://carnegieendowment.org/2021/03/24/europe-s-tightrope-diplomacy-on-china-pub-84159|dead-url=no}}</ref>、美国商会<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.uschamber.com/event/10th-china-business-conference|title=10th China Business Conference|last1=Washington|first1=U. S. Chamber of Commerce 1615 H. Street N.W.|last2=Maps|first2=D.C. 20062See map: Google|date=2019-02-28|website=U.S. Chamber of Commerce|language=en|access-date=2019-10-09|archive-date=2019-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190801213649/https://www.uschamber.com/event/10th-china-business-conference|dead-url=no}}</ref>、美国传统基金会、美国企业研究所和亚洲协会等学术机构举办的研讨会、论坛等学术交流活动。

每年，CCG会举办大型年会，“企业全球化论坛”和“中国与全球化论坛”，为来自中国政府、学术界和企业界的代表提供平台，就有关全球化的问题和中国在其中的作用进行对话和辩论。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://global.chinadaily.com.cn/a/201904/18/WS5cb7e068a3104842260b6e40.html|title=Globalization gains wide praise|website=[[China_Daily|China Daily]]|access-date=2019-10-09|dead-url=no|archive-date=2019-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191009161103/http://global.chinadaily.com.cn/a/201904/18/WS5cb7e068a3104842260b6e40.html}}</ref>

2018年7月，CCG作为一个非政府组织被授予[[联合国经济及社会理事会|联合国经济及社会理事会]]正式专门咨商地位。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.un.org/ecosoc/sites/www.un.org.ecosoc/files/documents/2018/decision.2018.252.pdf |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-05-14 |archive-date=2021-05-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210514005043/https://www.un.org/ecosoc/sites/www.un.org.ecosoc/files/documents/2018/decision.2018.252.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>11月，CCG受邀以指导委员会成员身份参加第一届“巴黎和平论坛”，并就全球治理创新提出两项建议。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://parispeaceforum.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Press-kit-Call-for-Projects-Paris-Peace-Forum-2019.pdf|title=Paris Peace Forum Press Kit|access-date=2019-10-15|archive-date=2019-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191009161052/https://parispeaceforum.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Press-kit-Call-for-Projects-Paris-Peace-Forum-2019.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>2019年，与卡内基-清华全球政策中心共同主办研讨会；在美国商会的中国商务会议上发表演讲；在慕尼黑安全会议期间主持讨论有关中欧合作的会议，这是中国组织智库首次举办官方的在慕尼黑安全会议会外活动举办官方边会；在世界经济论坛共同主办一次会议，探讨全球化的新方向和新动力。2019年7月，CCG被选为2020年国际大都市会议的主办单位。2020年11月24日，CCG主办、宾夕法尼亚大学智库研究项目（TTCSP）联合主办的第五届中国智库创新年会在北京举办<ref>{{Cite web|last=Zhu Bochen|date=Dec 3, 2020|title=Non-governmental think tanks to play a larger role in changing times|work=[[China.org.cn|China.org.cn]]|url=http://www.china.org.cn/china/2020-12/03/content_76973941.htm|access-date=April 26, 2021|archive-date=2020-12-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201221155148/http://www.china.org.cn/china/2020-12/03/content_76973941.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2020年12月8日，CCG在京主办大使圆桌会议。<ref>{{Cite news|last=中国网|date=Dec 9, 2020|title=几内亚比绍驻华大使馆参赞参加CCG大使圆桌论坛|work=[[中国网|中国网]]|url=http://www.china.com.cn/opinion/think/2020-12/09/content_76995254.htm|access-date=April 26, 2021|archive-date=2020-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201230175439/http://www.china.com.cn/opinion/think/2020-12/09/content_76995254.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

此外，自2020开始，CCG开启了“中国与世界”名家对话线上系列研讨会，邀请到了多位具有国际影响力的知名专家学者，如伦敦国王学院Kerry Brown教授<ref>{{Cite news|last=Kerry Brow|date=Mar 8, 2021|title=伦敦国王学院中国研究院院长：中国在很多方面值得西方借鉴|work=[[中国网|中国网]]|url=http://t.m.china.com.cn/convert/c_nwExWhyy.html|access-date=April 26, 2021|archive-date=2021-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210426185010/http://t.m.china.com.cn/convert/c_nwExWhyy.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，哈佛大学教授格雷厄姆·艾利森<ref>{{Cite news|last=格雷厄姆·艾利森、王辉耀|date=April 12, 2021|title=格雷厄姆·艾利森、王辉耀：超越“修昔底德陷阱”？从“澶渊之盟”到共商气候变化|work=[[中国网|中国网]]|url=https://www.guancha.cn/GrahamAlison/2021_04_12_587062.shtml|access-date=April 26, 2021|archive-date=2021-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210428213600/https://www.guancha.cn/GrahamAlison/2021_04_12_587062.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>，《世界是平的》作者、《纽约时报》专栏作家托马斯·弗里德曼等，共同探讨当下世界局势和全球化面临的困境以及中国在其中扮演的角色<ref>{{Cite news|last=严玉洁|date=April 1, 2021|title=美国学者：中国将保持开放，中美应加强对话与合作|work=[[中国日报|中国日报]]|url=https://cn.chinadaily.com.cn/a/202104/01/WS6065865fa3101e7ce97471fe.html|access-date=April 26, 2021|archive-date=2021-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210428201223/https://cn.chinadaily.com.cn/a/202104/01/WS6065865fa3101e7ce97471fe.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 地位和影响 ==
CCG也是中国人力资源和社会保障部认证的国家博士后项目研究中心。在宾夕法尼亚大学智库和公民社会项目（TTCSP）的“2020年全球智库指数”中，CCG在全球顶尖智库中排名第64位，在杰出的政策导向研究项目中排名第60位<ref name="#1">{{Cite web|last=James G.McGann|date=Jan 28, 2021|title=2020 Global Go To Think Tank Index Report|work=[[Think_Tank_And_Civil_Societies_Program_University_Of_Pennsylvania|Think Tank And Civil Societies Program University Of Pennsylvania]]|url=https://repository.upenn.edu/think_tanks/18/|access-date=April 21, 2021|archive-date=2021-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210612004515/https://repository.upenn.edu/think_tanks/18/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。曾获得过北京市民政局评选的“4A级社会组织”称号<ref>{{Cite web|last= Beijing Social Organization Evaluation Committee|date= November 20, 2019|title= Publicity of assessment results of Beijing Municipal Social Organizations in 2019|work= [[Beijing_Municipal_Civil_Affairs_Bureau|Beijing Municipal Civil Affairs Bureau]]|url= http://mzj.beijing.gov.cn/art/2019/11/20/art_371_294856.html|access-date= April 21, 2021|archive-date= 2021-04-11|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210411222700/http://mzj.beijing.gov.cn/art/2019/11/20/art_371_294856.html|dead-url= no}}</ref>。CCG拥有国家颁发的博士后科研工作站独立招收博士后的资质。在美国宾夕法尼亚大学智库与公民社会计划（TTCSP）发布的《2020年年度全球智库报告》中，CCG在全球顶级智库中排名第64位，在外交政策与国际事务智库排名中位列第60位，也是排列前50名的全球独立智库之一<ref name="#1"/>。

